<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 2. Euchelus erythraeensis Sturany, 1903, Locality 10 (Nawibi, Gulf of Aqaba, Red Sea). A-F, I. Lectotype, NHMW 37964: front (A-B), right side (C), top (D), back (E), bottom (F), protoconch (I). G. Original lectotype label. H. Original figure by Sturany (1903). Scale bars: A-F: 2 mm, I: 0.2 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/118637" .

